data.description: Are you looking for a spacious, modern home surrounded by beautiful Texas land? Look no further! This manufactured home offers 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms over 2100 sqft, making it the perfect space for families or those who love to entertain. With 5.5 acres of land and a quiet cul-de-sac location, this property offers endless potential for outdoor activities and relaxation. Don't miss out on this one-of-a-kind gem - schedule your visit today!
